#Hotelling Test
diab2 <- hotelling.test(Pregnancies + Glucose + BloodPressure + SkinThickness + Insulin + BMI + DiabetesPedigreeFunction + Age ~ Cat_Outcome, data = diabetes)
cat("T2 statistic =",diab2$stat[[1]],"\n")
